text: Stéphanie Brieussel (born 29 January 1974) is a French Olympic dressage rider. Representing France, she competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro where she finished 55th in the individual and 8th in the team competitions. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1974 births Category:French female equestrians Category:French dressage riders Category:Equestrians at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic equestrians of France
